name: Patchwork Kid
description:
A beautiful and unique addition to any room - brighten up a living room or add a sense of "I own art" to a dark hallway. Where ever you choose to hang this print, it wont disappoint. 

Each print is signed and numbered by the artist on the back, as well as digitally signed on the print itself.

8 1/2 by 11 Semi Gloss photo paper.
Fade resistant.
